dcterms:description: A new molecular dataset for developing machine learning models useful in chemistry and material science, comprising 12 quantum mechanical properties of 119,487 organic molecules with up to 14 heavy atoms, sampled from the GDB MedChem database.
dcterms:title: Alchemy

dcterms:description: A collection of various datasets for benchmarking machine learning models in molecular sciences, including a variety of supervised learning tasks.
dcterms:title: MoleculeNet

dcterms:description: The QM7 dataset contains 7,165 molecules, a subset of GDB-13, with at most 7 C, N, O, S atoms, used to predict a single electronic property, the atomization energy.
dcterms:title: QM7

dcterms:description: QM7b is an extension of QM7, containing 13 additional properties computed at different levels of accuracy.
dcterms:title: QM7b

dcterms:description: QM8 provides electronic properties of 21,786 molecules comprising up to 8 C, N, O, F atoms, including ground-state and excited-state properties.
dcterms:title: QM8

dcterms:description: QM9 contains geometric, energetic, electronic, and thermodynamic properties for 133,885 organic molecules comprising up to 9 non-hydrogen atoms.
dcterms:title: QM9
